songs.title: Jamie’s Sin
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Brrt
Yeah, sweet
Yeah, shit
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, some
Aye, aye
Yeah, shit, aye
Yeah, yeah, yeah, aye

[Verse 1]
Driving through the night on my ones I'm drifting (sweet)
Thinking 'bout you, I can't even handle this I'm liftin' (sweet)
I see all the quality around me even though I'm blind
Aye
She so fucking sexy, what a god damn mistress (right)
2 A.M., you all up in my god damn business (oh shit)
Fuck you, like I told you when I hit you up that time online
Yeah
Watching how you moving is a motherfucking art piece (sweet)
Slowly you'll be mine like a motherfucking car lease (shit)
Chasin' all my problems down the valley, I don't got no time
Yeah
Pickin' out your flaws just to prove that I ain't dreamin' (dream)
I'm a lost cause, why they think a nigga teachin' (oh shit)
Copy all these words just to read it later when I die
Yeah

[Hook]
Jamie wasn't Jamie when she drank up all the Jameson (drink)
I devote my time just so I could fuckin' let this in (drink)
Caught me slippin' when you saw me out of place again (sweet)
Yeah
Jamie wasn't Jamie when she drank up all the Jameson (sin)
Jamie, Jamie, Jamie drank up all the Jameson (sweet)
Jamie, Jamie, Jamie drank up all the Jameson

[Outro]
Aye, know what I'm saying
Sweet, brrt
Sin
Drink
